OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"The longer you're here, it's hard to
OL,7,Fsee the daylight at the end of the
OL,8,Ftunnel," one inmate at HMP Highpoint
OL,9,Ftold ITV News.
OL,11,F"There's not really much to make
OL,12,Fpeople change," admitted another.
OL,13,F"You're just forgotten about".
OL,15,FWe were given rare television access
OL,16,Finto Highpoint, a category C men's
OL,17,Fprison in Suffolk.
