OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,FThe prison holds criminals convicted
OL,7,Fof non-violent offences like drug-
OL,8,Frelated crimes, burglary and theft -
OL,9,Fwith sentences ranging from a few
OL,10,Fweeks, to life orders.
OL,12,FHighpoint holds exactly the kind of
OL,13,Finmates the government thinks should
OL,14,Fbe spending more time serving
OL,15,Fcommunity orders, rather than in
OL,16,Fprison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
