OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,FAfter an overcrowding crisis in
OL,7,FBritain's jails that peaked in the
OL,8,Fsummer, the new Labour government
OL,9,Fstarted trying to tackle the problem
OL,10,Fby releasing thousands of prisoners
OL,11,Fearly, and launching a review of
OL,12,Fsentencing.
OL,14,FRoss Payton, who has served four years
OL,15,Fof a longer sentence for supplying
OL,16,Fdrugs, said he doesn't think lengthy
OL,17,Fsentences work.
OL,19,F"The first four years I've changed
OL,20,Fenough as it is, I don't think I need
OL,21,Fto do more time," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
