OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"I believe if people had closer ties
OL,7,Fto their family, and being able to
OL,8,Fwork and stuff and still earn money,
OL,9,Fit would help a lot more than just
OL,10,Fbeing stuck away from normal life for
OL,11,Fsuch a long time".
OL,13,FBecause jails are full to the brim,
OL,14,FHMP Highpoint is being expanded, with
OL,15,Fwork to build 700 new places starting
OL,16,Fthis week. The expansion will make it
OL,17,Fthe largest prison in the UK.
OL,19,FThe project is part of the
OL,20,Fgovernment's pledge to deliver 14,000
OL,21,Fextra prison places by 2031.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
