OL,6,FMany inmates are now forced to share
OL,7,Fcells designed for one person -
OL,8,F"there's too many people" according to
OL,9,FRoss.
OL,11,F"We need tough sentences outside of
OL,12,Fprisons": Prisons Minister tells
OL,13,FShehab Khan
OL,15,F"We need prisons to be tough... we
OL,16,Falso need tough sentences outside of
OL,17,Fprisons," Prisons Minister Lord
OL,18,FTimpson told ITV News Political
OL,19,FCorrespondent Shehab Khan.
