OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,FFormer CEO of shoe repair chain
OL,7,FTimpson's, Lord Timpson was a surprise
OL,8,Fappointment when Sir Keir Starmer put
OL,9,Fhim in charge of Britain's jails after
OL,10,Fthe election in July 2024.
OL,12,FHis boss, Justice Secretary Shabana
OL,13,FMahmood, travelled to Texas recently
OL,14,Fto see their successful prison system
OL,15,Fand get ideas about solving the crisis
OL,16,Fin Britain's prisons.
OL,18,F"We need to find, whether it's in the
OL,19,FUK or abroad, things that work, and
OL,20,Fsee how we can bring those here,''
OL,21,FTimpson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
