OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"One of the prisons the Lord
OL,7,FChancellor went to, they had a re-
OL,8,Foffending rate of 17%, we can only
OL,9,Fdream of 17%".
OL,11,FBefore his appointment to the
OL,12,Fgovernment, Timpson controversially
OL,13,Fsaid that only a "third of prisoners
OL,14,Fshould be behind bars" and that
OL,15,FBritain is "addicted to punishment".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
