OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,FInmates at HMP Highpoint have access
OL,7,Fto a number of employment and training
OL,8,Fschemes - ranging from railway
OL,9,Fmaintenance, to electronic waste
OL,10,Frecycling.
OL,12,FBut we heard from staff running the
OL,13,Fschemes and inmates inside that the
OL,14,Fprogrammes are oversubscribed, with
OL,15,Fone scheme having a waiting list of
OL,16,Fover 100.
OL,18,F"We need to do more": Timpson on
OL,19,Fprison training schemes
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
