OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"'There's so many people in the prison
OL,7,Fat the minute, it's hard to get on the
OL,8,Fcourses," Ross said.
OL,10,FWhen asked about the long waiting
OL,11,Flists for the schemes, Timpson told
OL,12,Fus: "I think it's brilliant that
OL,13,Fpeople are queuing up, but we need to
OL,14,Fdo more."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
