OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,FBut at a time where government
OL,7,Fdepartments are being urged to make
OL,8,Fcuts by the Treasury, he accepted that
OL,9,Fproviding more places on the schemes
OL,10,F"costs money" and there's not enough
OL,11,Fspace for training facilities in
OL,12,Falready crowded jails.
OL,14,F"One of the problems we have,
OL,15,Fespecially with our Victorian prisons,
OL,16,Fis we've now got two people in a cell
OL,17,Fthat's booked for one and we don't
OL,18,Fhave enough workshop space," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
