OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"The Chancellor has got some difficult
OL,7,Fdecisions to make, and what our job in
OL,8,Fthe Ministry of Justice to do is to
OL,9,Fput forward a strong argument, but
OL,10,Fit's up to others to decide," Timpson
OL,11,Ftold Shehab.
OL,13,FWe spoke to one inmate who is also in
OL,14,Fprison for drug offences, and has been
OL,15,Fgiven a job inside the jail, leading a
OL,16,Fteam of other prisoners recycling
OL,17,Felectronic waste.
