OL,3,C'It's hard to see light at the end of
OL,4,Cthe tunnel': Inside HMP Highpoint
OL,6,F"I've got a good job here, I'm doing
OL,7,Fmy time and I'm doing my punishment,
OL,8,Fbut I'm doing it in a nice way," the
OL,9,Finmate, who did not want to be named,
OL,10,Ftold us.
OL,12,F"The longer you're here, it's hard to
OL,13,Fsee the daylight at the end of the
OL,14,Ftunnel - so if they get you onto
OL,15,Fmeaningful things, then it's got to be
OL,16,Fbetter surely," he said.
